OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FITV News Correspondent John Ray heard
OL,8,Ffrom some of the veterans who say it's
OL,9,Ftime to right the wrongs of the past.
OL,11,FThis report contains language and
OL,12,Freferences to attitudes that some may
OL,13,Ffind distressing
OL,15,FFor a group of British ex-service
OL,16,Fpersonnel, this is one final battle
OL,17,Fthey never thought they'd fight, nor
OL,18,Fone they now particularly relish. For
OL,19,Fit is reigniting painful memories.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FBut it is, they say, a matter of
OL,8,Fhonour and duty to their comrades.
OL,10,F"I've turned my back on this for
OL,11,Fthirty years," Steve Stewart said, a
OL,12,Fformer corporal in the Royal Military
OL,13,FPolice.
OL,15,F"It was so humiliating and
OL,16,Fembarrassing for me."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@NO]wD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FHe served his country with distinction
OL,8,Fin Iraq and Northern Ireland, but was
OL,9,Fforced out of the army after being
OL,10,Faccused of breaking the very
OL,11,Fregulations he'd sworn to uphold.
OL,13,FDespite being decriminalised back in
OL,14,F1967, homosexuality in the armed
OL,15,Fforces remained illegal until 2000.
OL,17,FSteve's "outing" was an ordeal. His
OL,18,Fcommanding officer told him he
OL,19,Fdisgusted him. He was threatened with
OL,20,Fprosecution and public disgrace.
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"I was given the opportunity of taking
OL,8,Fone of two doors," he told me. Both
OL,9,Fled to the loss of the career he
OL,10,Floved, but one involved less pain.
OL,12,F"One would have been through court
OL,13,Fmartial, prison and dishonourable
OL,14,Fdischarge. The other was, 'You can buy
OL,15,Fyourself out, and we'll say nothing
OL,16,Fmore about it.'"
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@RO]tD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FSo Steve left "voluntarily". But
OL,8,Fdecades on, that decision means he's
OL,9,Fineligible for the full compensation
OL,10,Fof #50,000 the Ministry of Defence is
OL,11,Foffering LGBT veterans who were
OL,12,Fofficially discharged from the service.
OL,14,FThe distinction - critics call it "two-
OL,15,Ftier" justice - is now the subject of
OL,16,Fa legal challenge in the High Court,
OL,17,Fin which Steve is a lead claimant.
OL,19,FThere are thought to be hundreds more
OL,20,Fveterans ready to stake their claims
OL,21,Fif he succeeds.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@[O]vD@cOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
