OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FAmong them is Gary Wilson, whose
OL,8,Fexperience is a shocking reminder of
OL,9,Fthe prejudice and cruelty of times not
OL,10,Fthat long in the past.
OL,12,FHe describes himself as a naive
OL,13,Fnineteen-year-old when he fulfilled
OL,14,Fhis boyhood dream to follow his father
OL,15,Finto the RAF.
OL,17,FBut the dream lasted just two weeks
OL,18,Fbefore suspicions about his sexuality
OL,19,Fwere raised by fellow recruits.
OL,26,@tD@]xt
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
