PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"Somebody urinated all over my bed,
OL,8,Fand everyone was laughing," he
OL,9,Fremembered. He said he was made to
OL,10,Ffeel "dirty, like there's something
OL,11,Fwrong" with him.
OL,13,FHe would look in vain for sympathy
OL,14,Ffrom his officer.
OL,16,F"He said, 'You're probably into
OL,17,Fchildren and boys and things like
OL,18,Fthat.' And I just got upset, and he
OL,19,Fsaid, 'This proves you can't act like
OL,20,Fa man - you're crying.'"
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@[O]rD@FOUsD@FO]xD@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
