OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FLike Steve, Gary has been told he
OL,8,Fdoesn't qualify for full compensation
OL,9,Fbecause he too is deemed to have
OL,10,Fresigned. He vehemently disputes that
OL,11,Fclaim.
OL,13,F"I didn't have a choice. I couldn't
OL,14,Fstay, or I'd have been in military
OL,15,Fprison."
OL,17,FThe end of the ban came about after a
OL,18,Fruling by the European Court of Human
OL,19,FRights.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
