OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Defence had spent
OL,8,Fyears arguing to keep the legislation
OL,9,Fin place, resisting pressure from
OL,10,Fcampaign groups and lobbying by MPs.
OL,12,FOne of its main arguments was that
OL,13,FLGBT personnel were more vulnerable to
OL,14,Fblackmail, according to Dr Daniel
OL,15,FLomas, Assistant Professor in
OL,16,FInternational Relations at the
OL,17,FUniversity of Nottingham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
