OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FHe said: "It had always been a
OL,8,Fspecific concern for the security
OL,9,Fservice about individuals with access
OL,10,Fto secret information, who could
OL,11,Fpotentially be compromised because
OL,12,Fthey could pass information to a
OL,13,Fforeign intelligence service."
OL,15,FVito Ward, a Women's Royal Naval
OL,16,FService veteran, said she was left
OL,17,Ffeeling "numb" when she was discharged
OL,18,Fin 1970.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FShe was brought in front of her senior
OL,8,Fofficer and shown photocopies of
OL,9,Fletters she had written to a former
OL,10,Fpartner.
OL,12,FVito is among those who have received
OL,13,Ffull compensation, something she told
OL,14,Fus remains inaccessible to many others
OL,15,Fwho struggle to reopen old wounds.
OL,17,F"Applying is so painful, but there's
OL,18,Fstill people being rejected on top of
OL,19,Fthat," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
