OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"Those people never got the
OL,8,Fopportunity to reclaim their veteran
OL,9,Fstatus, and to reclaim the pride of
OL,10,Fgiving service to the country."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
