OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Defence will not
OL,8,Fcomment on individual cases, but it
OL,9,Ftold us: "We deeply regret the
OL,10,Ftreatment of LGBT serving personnel
OL,11,Fbetween 1967 and 2000, which was
OL,12,Fwholly unacceptable and is not
OL,13,Frepresentative of Defence today.
OL,15,F"We are committed to righting these
OL,16,Fwrongs through tangible actions,
OL,17,Fincluding through the LGBT financial
OL,18,Fand non-financial restorative measures
OL,19,Ffor those affected."
OL,26,@qD@JOUwD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780611061
OL,3,C'It was humiliating': LGBT veterans
OL,4,Ctake 'two-tier' compensation scheme to
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe rationale of the "two-tier" scheme
OL,8,Fis that those who were dishonourably
OL,9,Fdischarged faced greater difficulties
OL,10,Ffinding work and rebuilding their
OL,11,Flives on civvy street.
OL,13,FBut what is clear is that both Steve
OL,14,Fand Gary still carry the scars - that
OL,15,Fdecades on, the past is still
OL,16,Fpainfully present.
OL,18,F"It's about everybody being treated
OL,19,Ffairly and the same," Gary said. "It's
OL,20,Fabout whether we're worthy. And if
OL,21,Fwe're not worthy, why not?"
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@_O]zD@AOU{D@UO]{D@bOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
